---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Tentang Saya & Profil" description="Profil tentang Fatahilah Miftahul Rahman, lulusan SMK Patriot Pituruh jurusan TKJ (2026), Juara 1 LKS IT Network System Administration, serta praktisi AI Prompt Engineering.">
  <section class="about-section container section-py">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-badge">
        <span class="badge font-mono" data-i18n="nav.about">Tentang Saya</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-heading" data-i18n="about.title">About Me & Profil Profesional</h1>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Memadukan keahlian administrasi jaringan & sistem server dengan inovasi otomatisasi berbasis AI Prompt Engineering.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main About Grid (Exact Source from ~/storage/shared/portofolio/index.html) -->
    <div class="about-grid">
      <!-- Left Column: Biography -->
      <div class="about-bio glass-card">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-4">Latar Belakang & Visi Teknologi</h2>
        <div class="bio-content leading-relaxed text-muted space-y-4">
          <p>
            Saya lulusan SMK Patriot Pituruh jurusan Teknik Komputer dan Jaringan (2026) dengan spesialisasi di bidang IT Network & System Administration. Prestasi terbaik saya adalah meraih Juara 1 pada Lomba Kompetensi Siswa (LKS) SMK tingkat Kabupaten Purworejo di bidang IT Network System Administration.
          </p>
          <p>
            Saat ini, saya tidak hanya fokus pada infrastruktur jaringan dan manajemen server, tetapi juga mendalami AI Prompt Engineering. Saya melihat potensi besar AI untuk mengotomatisasi skrip jaringan dan troubleshooting sistem, sehingga pekerjaan di industri bisa menjadi lebih efisien, cepat, dan aman.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bio-actions mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-border flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/experience" class="btn-primary">Lihat Pengalaman PKL →</a>
          <a href="/skills" class="btn-secondary">Daftar Keahlian Teknis →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Meta Info & Achievement Cards -->
      <div class="about-meta flex flex-col gap-6">
        <!-- Pendidikan Card -->
        <div class="meta-card glass-card">
          <div class="meta-icon font-mono">🎓 Pendidikan</div>
          <h3 class="meta-title font-heading">SMK Patriot Pituruh</h3>
          <p class="meta-val font-mono text-muted">Teknik Komputer dan Jaringan (TKJ)</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Tahun Lulus Card -->
        <div class="meta-card glass-card">
          <div class="meta-icon font-mono">📅 Tahun Lulus</div>
          <h3 class="meta-title font-heading">Angkatan 2026</h3>
          <p class="meta-val font-mono text-muted">Siap Kerja & Berkembang di Industri IT</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Prestasi LKS Featured Card -->
        <div class="achievement-card glass-card">
          <div class="achievement-badge font-mono badge badge-gold">🏆 Prestasi Utama</div>
          <h3 class="achievement-title font-heading mt-2">Lomba Kompetensi Siswa (LKS) SMK</h3>
          <div class="achievement-val font-mono text-accent text-lg font-bold">Juara I</div>
          <p class="meta-val font-mono text-muted mt-1">IT Network System Administration<br>Tingkat Kabupaten Purworejo, 2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Core Philosophy / Focus Areas -->
    <div class="focus-areas mt-16">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-center mb-8">Fokus & Kompetensi Utama</h2>
      <div class="focus-grid">
        <div class="focus-item glass-card">
          <span class="focus-num font-mono">01</span>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl">Network Infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mt-2">Perancangan dan pengamanan topologi jaringan LAN, WLAN, VLAN, routing, serta konfigurasi RouterBoard MikroTik & Cisco.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-item glass-card">
          <span class="focus-num font-mono">02</span>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl">Server Administration</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mt-2">Instalasi & optimalisasi Linux Debian Server (DNS, Web Server Nginx/Apache, DHCP, Nftables Firewall, dan High Availability HAProxy).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-item glass-card">
          <span class="focus-num font-mono">03</span>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl">AI Prompt Engineering</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mt-2">Pemanfaatan Large Language Models (LLM) untuk pembuatan otomatisasi skrip administrasi jaringan dan percepatan analisis troubleshooting.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .section-header { text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 48px; }
  .section-badge { margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .section-subtitle { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 12px; }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
    gap: 32px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-bio {
    padding: 36px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .bio-content p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .meta-card,
  .achievement-card {
    padding: 24px 28px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .meta-card:hover,
  .achievement-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .achievement-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-card) 0%, rgba(255, 179, 0, 0.05) 100%);
  }

  .meta-icon {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .meta-title,
  .achievement-title {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
  }

  .meta-val {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* Focus areas */
  .focus-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .focus-item {
    padding: 28px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .focus-num {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-bio { padding: 24px; }
  }
</style>
